data.description: Welcome home to 349 Live Oak Church Road! This 4 bedroom 2.5 bath charming & spacious home is situated comfortably right outside of the hustle & bustle but just minutes away from everything you need (including Ft Stewart Gate 7)! Enjoy the community pool & playground that Griffin Park has to offer or retreat to your fully fenced in sizeable backyard. Step inside to the captivating 2-story foyer & benefit all this home has to offer! To include the roomy formal living room (utilize however you see fit!), separate dining room, generously sized kitchen with ample cabinets & counter space for all your cooking needs & stainless steel appliances, exceptional breakfast area with more cabinets/counter space & continuing into your massive great room! Proceed upstairs to discover all 4 pleasantly sized bedrooms, grand primary bathroom and closet, guest bathroom & laundry room!
